{
  "page": "Starfall",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Starfall</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nCastle</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Starfall_by_Eddie_Mendoza.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Starfall by Eddie Mendoza.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Starfall_by_Eddie_Mendoza.jpg/350px-Starfall_by_Eddie_Mendoza.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"262\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cd/Starfall_by_Eddie_Mendoza.jpg/525px-Starfall_by_Eddie_Mendoza.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cd/Starfall_by_Eddie_Mendoza.jpg/700px-Starfall_by_Eddie_Mendoza.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Starfall, by Eddie Mendoza for the <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Calendar\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar\">A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar</a></i>  © Bantam Books</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Government</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Ruler</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Edric_Dayne\" title=\"Edric Dayne\">Edric Dayne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Religion</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Named for</th><td>\nA falling star</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Notable places</th><td>\nPalestone Sword</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dorne.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Dorne and the location of Starfall\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of Starfall\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/350px-Dorne.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"168\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/525px-Dorne.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f5/Dorne.png/700px-Dorne.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 56.7%; left: 6.7%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"Dorne and the location of Starfall\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Starfall\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 80%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Starfall</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> and the location of Starfall\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/98/Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png/300px-Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"198\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/98/Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png/450px-Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/98/Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png/600px-Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sebastian_Giacobino_Palestone_Sword_Guard_II.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Palestone Sword Guard, by Sebastian Giacobino © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png/300px-Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"196\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png/450px-Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png/600px-Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Starfall_HealerBruce_Moffet.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a> at Starfall harvests flowers, by Bruce Moffet © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Starfall</b> is the ancestral castle of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Older_History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Older History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Targaryen_Era\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Targaryen Era</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Starfall\" title=\"Category:Images of Starfall\">Images of Starfall</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Starfall is located in the western <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Mountains\" title=\"Red Mountains\">Red Mountains</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> on an island in the <a href=\"/index.php/Torentine\" title=\"Torentine\">Torentine</a> where it pours into the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Sea\" title=\"Summer Sea\">Summer Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafstarfall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafstarfall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The castle includes a tower called the Palestone Sword.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Northeast of Starfall is <a href=\"/index.php/High_Hermitage\" title=\"High Hermitage\">High Hermitage</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> the seat of a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne_of_High_Hermitage\" title=\"House Dayne of High Hermitage\">lesser branch</a> of House Dayne.<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Older_History\">Older History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Older History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>According to legend, Starfall was built where the first <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">Dayne</a> found a <a href=\"/index.php/Dawn\" title=\"Dawn\">magic stone</a> after he followed the path of a shooting star. The Daynes grew in power to become the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Torrentine\" title=\"King of the Torrentine\">Kings of the Torrentine</a> and one of the strongest houses of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_kingdoms_of_the_first_men.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The Daynes submitted to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Nymeros Martell</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria%27s_War\" title=\"Nymeria&#39;s War\">Nymeria's War</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Targaryen_Era\">Targaryen Era</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Targaryen Era\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Dayne\" title=\"Joffrey Dayne\">Joffrey Dayne</a> attacked <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> burned Starfall with her dragon, <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_dorne_against_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a> and Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Martell\" title=\"Elia Martell\">Elia Martell</a> visited Starfall on their way to <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> where their mother was to broker their marriage to the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> twins, <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the aftermath of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Sword_of_the_Morning\" title=\"Sword of the Morning\">Sword of the Morning</a>, perished at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_joy\" title=\"Tower of joy\">tower of joy</a>. When Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> returned Arthur's sword, the ancestral blade <a href=\"/index.php/Dawn\" title=\"Dawn\">Dawn</a>, to Starfall, Arthur's sister <a href=\"/index.php/Ashara_Dayne\" title=\"Ashara Dayne\">Ashara</a> threw herself from the castle's Palestone Sword tower.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Starfall is the subject of the cover of the 2025 <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Calendar\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar\">A Song of Ice and Fire Calendar</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Starfall&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Catelyn II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafwesteros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Westeros.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafstarfall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafstarfall.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_